{"release_time": "2026-02-19T15:00:52+0800", "update_time": "2026-02-19T15:01:03+0800", "description": {"title": "豆瓣影视榜单列表", "subtitle": "最近热门日剧", "source": "https://m.douban.com/subject_collection/tv_japanese", "link": "https://m.douban.com/rexxar/api/v2/subject_collection/tv_japanese/items", "page_start": 1, "page_end": 1, "page_total": 1, "page_limit": -1, "item_total": null, "item_limit": 20, "page_count": 1, "sup_page_count": 0}, "extra": {}, "stats": {"movies": 20}, "movies": [{"comment": "累计发行量突破1160万部，在文学史上散发着孤高光辉的北方谦三的历史大河小说《水浒传》，全19卷将在WOWOW完全映像化。故事发生在北宋末期（12世纪初）的中国，志同道合的汉人们聚集在“梁山泊”，为了纠正腐败的社会而勇敢地站起来。在本作品中担任主演的是至今为止引领日本电影、电视剧界的织田裕二，他饰演梁山泊的头领宋江。", "rating": {"count": 0, "max": 10, "star_count": 0.0, "value": 0}, "vendor_count": 0, "has_linewatch": false, "pic": {"large": "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2928303377.jpg", "normal": "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2928303377.jpg"}, "honor_infos": [], "uri": "douban://douban.com/tv/37039217", "episodes_info": "", "photos": ["https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2927938983.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2926395552.jpg", "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2924672976.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2928303373.jpg"], "vendor_icons": [], "interest": null, "year": "2026", "card_subtitle": "2026 / 日本 / 剧情 历史 战争 / 若松节朗 村谷嘉则 佐藤さやか / 织田裕二 反町隆史", "title": "北方谦三 水浒传", "type": "tv", "id": "37039217", "tags": []}, {"comment": "掌握专业技能却不善言辞、连假笑都勉强不了的加纳彰人（醍醐虎汰朗 饰），被从系统工程师调到销售岗位，在部门里总显得格格不入。某天又因一点小争执，惹恼了自己暗恋的同事大狼诚司（中川大辅 饰）。心情低落时，他在神社的台阶上不慎跌落，醒来后却发现身处一个截然不同的世界：同事们主动亲切地和他说话，大狼更是投来炽热的目光——对彰人来说无比舒适的“如果的世界”就此展开…\n本剧改编自海野幸的同名原著小说。", "rating": {"count": 8039, "max": 10, "star_count": 4.0, "value": 8.0}, "vendor_count": 0, "has_linewatch": false, "pic": {"large": "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2926960904.jpg", "normal": "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2926960904.jpg"}, "honor_infos": [], "uri": "douban://douban.com/tv/37562506", "episodes_info": "", "photos": ["https://img2.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2927522051.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2928019533.jpg", "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2928038440.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2928290492.jpg"], "vendor_icons": [], "interest": null, "year": "2025", "card_subtitle": "2025 / 日本 / 爱情 同性 奇幻 / 针生悠伺 安川徳寛 / 醍醐虎汰朗 中川大辅", "title": "在如果的世界里开始恋爱", "type": "tv", "id": "37562506", "tags": []}, {"comment": "感情不外露的横井凑（吉泽要人 饰），与一切情绪都写在脸上的中乃航（雨宫翔 饰），看似性格相反，却因共同的摄影兴趣而成为挚友，并在大学时期同居。随着凑就业，两人不得不结束同居生活，航这才意识到自己对挚友的感情早已超越友情。数年后，两人以社会人身份重逢——一个“想要继续做朋友”的凑，一个“无论如何都想成为恋人”的航，从彼此的单恋开始，一段暖心又酸涩的双向暗恋喜剧就此展开。\n本剧改编自ろじ的同名原著漫画。", "rating": {"count": 725, "max": 10, "star_count": 3.5, "value": 7.2}, "vendor_count": 0, "has_linewatch": false, "pic": {"large": "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2928951634.jpg", "normal": "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2928951634.jpg"}, "honor_infos": [], "uri": "douban://douban.com/tv/37660498", "episodes_info": "", "photos": ["https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2928951890.jpg", "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2928951889.jpg", "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2928951888.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2928951887.jpg"], "vendor_icons": [], "interest": null, "year": "2026", "card_subtitle": "2026 / 日本 / 爱情 同性 / 船曳真珠 野村奈绪 岸田雅喜 / 吉泽要人 雨宫翔", "title": "直到对挚友的“要不要同居”说出“好”", "type": "tv", "id": "37660498", "tags": []}, {"comment": "故事是〈宇宙并非只有一个。多个重叠的多元宇宙，也存在着与我们居住的地球相似的另一个地球――。〉以多元宇宙论的世界观发展故事。\n主人公「卡邦·无限」是能够超越次元的宇宙刑事。在各种各样的次元为舞台里会怎样解决事件？而且为什么卡邦·无限能够超越次元？……从未有人看过的新卡邦传说开幕！", "rating": {"count": 0, "max": 10, "star_count": 0.0, "value": 0}, "vendor_count": 0, "has_linewatch": false, "pic": {"large": "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2928385416.jpg", "normal": "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2928385416.jpg"}, "honor_infos": [], "uri": "douban://douban.com/tv/37855634", "episodes_info": "", "photos": ["https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929956190.jpg", "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929956189.jpg", "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929956188.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929956187.jpg"], "vendor_icons": [], "interest": null, "year": "2026", "card_subtitle": "2026 / 日本 / 剧情 动作 科幻 / 福泽博文 / 长田光平 赤羽流河", "title": "超宇宙刑事卡邦 无限", "type": "tv", "id": "37855634", "tags": []}, {"comment": "一命一分，生死赌局。\n序幕揭开，众武士在动荡时代浴血奋战。\n时值19世纪末明治时期，包括嵯峨愁二郎（冈田准一 饰）在内的 292 位武士受到丰厚奖金吸引，深夜齐聚京都天龙寺，参加一场宛如人间炼狱的比赛：每人分得一块木札，唯有夺取他人木札并率先抵达东京，方能获得奖金。夜幕低垂，寺院内弥漫诡谲气息，嗜血武士蠢蠢欲动。随着比赛号令一响，武士立刻展开血腥而残酷的生存之战。", "rating": {"count": 7538, "max": 10, "star_count": 3.5, "value": 7.3}, "vendor_count": 0, "has_linewatch": false, "pic": {"large": "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2926538607.jpg", "normal": "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2926538607.jpg"}, "honor_infos": [{"kind": "tv", "uri": "douban://douban.com/subject_collection/ECNA46YBA?type=rank&category=movie&rank_type=tv_genre", "rank": 4, "title": "近期热门日剧榜"}], "uri": "douban://douban.com/tv/36864544", "episodes_info": "", "photos": ["https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2927004057.jpg", "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2927004050.jpg", "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2927004054.jpg", "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2927437240.jpg"], "vendor_icons": [], "interest": null, "year": "2025", "card_subtitle": "2025 / 日本 / 剧情 动作 惊悚 历史 / 藤井道人 山口健人 山本透 / 冈田准一 藤崎由美亚", "title": "武士生死斗", "type": "tv", "id": "36864544", "tags": []}, {"comment": "主人公长谷大河曾是备受期待的大学田径新星，却因成绩不佳而结束了跑步生涯。如今他在小料理店\"田实\"打工，当店主让他负责开发新菜品时，他逐渐在工作中找到了价值。另一边，为学习动画专程从韩国来日留学的研究生朴琳，终日为课题创作奔波。好不容易在截止日前提交作品，却收到宿舍解约通知要求搬离。在东京找房并非易事，琳逐渐身心俱疲。机缘巧合下，二人在\"田实\"相遇。琳品尝了大河亲手捏的饭团后深受感动，疲惫的身心都被这份温暖治愈。而大河则被琳享用美食时灿烂的笑容深深吸引。", "rating": {"count": 875, "max": 10, "star_count": 3.5, "value": 6.8}, "vendor_count": 0, "has_linewatch": false, "pic": {"large": "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2929168828.jpg", "normal": "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2929168828.jpg"}, "honor_infos": [], "uri": "douban://douban.com/tv/37645091", "episodes_info": "", "photos": ["https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929339575.jpg", "https://img2.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929783521.jpg", "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929783520.jpg", "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929783519.jpg"], "vendor_icons": [], "interest": null, "year": "2026", "card_subtitle": "2026 / 日本 / 爱情 / 林田浩川 畑中みゆき 小山亮太 / 赤楚卫二 姜惠元", "title": "紫菜包饭和饭团～相爱的两个人相似又不一样～", "type": "tv", "id": "37645091", "tags": []}, {"comment": "东京电视台现象级悬疑惊悚系列《TXQ FICTION》第四弹重磅来袭，继继《TXQ FICTION寻找石永菊江》《TXQ FICTION向饭沼一家谢罪》等高分作品引爆话题后，主创团队再度深耕伪纪录片叙事肌理，以“UFO”这一充满未知与敬畏的命题，编织一场交织浪漫与恐惧的神秘迷局。", "rating": {"count": 1575, "max": 10, "star_count": 3.0, "value": 5.8}, "vendor_count": 0, "has_linewatch": false, "pic": {"large": "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2928217277.jpg", "normal": "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2928217277.jpg"}, "honor_infos": [], "uri": "douban://douban.com/tv/37936954", "episodes_info": "", "photos": ["https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2928229560.jpg", "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2928229559.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2928229557.jpg", "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2928229556.jpg"], "vendor_icons": [], "interest": null, "year": "2025", "card_subtitle": "2025 / 日本 / 科幻 悬疑 惊悚 恐怖 / 近藤亮太 大森時生 寺内康太郎 皆口大地", "title": "TXQ FICTION UFO之山", "type": "tv", "id": "37936954", "tags": []}, {"comment": "王子般完美、气质值拉满的超级家庭教师岸骑士（泽村玲 饰），被彻的母亲请来为成绩长期垫底、每天只会打架的重度不良少年高杉彻（田中洸希 饰）补习。岸外表俊美、举止优雅，对彻的指导却温柔甜蜜，宛如“甜度过量”的王子降临。彻原本强硬桀骜，却逐渐被岸的魅力带乱节奏，生活也随之发生改变。作品以闪耀喜剧风格为基调，带有轻微BL氛围，描绘了两人之间奇妙又令人心动的互动。\n本剧改编自奥嶋ひろまさ的同名原著漫画。", "rating": {"count": 686, "max": 10, "star_count": 3.5, "value": 7.4}, "vendor_count": 0, "has_linewatch": false, "pic": {"large": "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2927464124.jpg", "normal": "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2927464124.jpg"}, "honor_infos": [], "uri": "douban://douban.com/tv/37812763", "episodes_info": "", "photos": ["https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2928387772.jpg", "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929071404.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929071403.jpg", "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929071370.jpg"], "vendor_icons": [], "interest": null, "year": "2026", "card_subtitle": "2026 / 日本 / 剧情 喜剧 同性 / 上村奈帆 野村奈绪 永江二朗 Jirô Nagae / 沢村玲 田中洸希", "title": "我是家庭教师岸骑士", "type": "tv", "id": "37812763", "tags": []}, {"comment": "23年前，小学六年级的飞奈淳一（竹内凉真 饰）与关系要好的三名同学，共同把一把卷入事件的手枪埋在樱树下。成年后，淳一成为刑警，却在某起案件中得知：凶器正是当年四人一起埋下的那把枪。更令他震动的是，他以刑警与嫌疑人的身份，与初恋岩本万季子（井上真央 饰）再会。随着调查推进，他逐一与当年的伙伴重逢，被掩埋的真相、背叛与秘密逐渐浮现。过往的“再会”，将彻底改变所有人的人生轨迹。\n本剧改编自横关大的同名原著小说。", "rating": {"count": 830, "max": 10, "star_count": 3.5, "value": 7.3}, "vendor_count": 0, "has_linewatch": false, "pic": {"large": "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2928087176.jpg", "normal": "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2928087176.jpg"}, "honor_infos": [], "uri": "douban://douban.com/tv/37855030", "episodes_info": "", "photos": ["https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929051169.jpg", "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929051166.jpg", "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2928969565.jpg", "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2928969566.jpg"], "vendor_icons": [], "interest": null, "year": "2026", "card_subtitle": "2026 / 日本 / 剧情 爱情 悬疑 / 深川荣洋 山本大辅 / 竹内凉真 井上真央", "title": "再会～沉默的真相～", "type": "tv", "id": "37855030", "tags": []}, {"comment": "性情温和的糕点师早濑陆（松山研一 饰）与妻子夏海、儿子和母亲经营“早濑洋菓子店”。但两年半前妻子失踪，后被发现遇害，早濑却被诬为凶手。与此同时，警视厅刑警仪堂步（铃木亮平 饰）登场——他是不择手段、与黑社会勾结的恶警。面对绝境，早濑决心洗清罪名，重启人生，化身为仪堂追查真凶。夏海的前同事、会计师幸后一香（户田惠梨香 饰）协助他整容改貌，但她的真实意图仍笼罩在谜团之中。", "rating": {"count": 657, "max": 10, "star_count": 3.5, "value": 6.5}, "vendor_count": 0, "has_linewatch": false, "pic": {"large": "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2929142530.jpg", "normal": "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2929142530.jpg"}, "honor_infos": [], "uri": "douban://douban.com/tv/37434113", "episodes_info": "", "photos": ["https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929104819.jpg", "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2927381026.jpg", "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929955900.jpg", "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929955899.jpg"], "vendor_icons": [], "interest": null, "year": "2026", "card_subtitle": "2026 / 日本 / 剧情 悬疑 犯罪 / 坪井敏雄 田中健太 元井桃 / 铃木亮平 户田惠梨香", "title": "重启", "type": "tv", "id": "37434113", "tags": []}, {"comment": "乡下温泉街“西谷温泉”里，侦探兼发明家一之濑洋辅（松田龙平 饰）住在自家废弃的老旅馆，并将这里改造成充满离奇发明品的侦探事务所。曾在美国成功开发“将负面情绪转化为能量”的技术，使小镇出现许多不可思议的装置。每天都有性格独特的居民带来奇怪却温暖的委托，洋辅便以异想天开的机制与奇招处理难题。一桩桩古怪事件在笑声中解决，也让人与人之间的羁绊在这座温泉街悄然升温。", "rating": {"count": 893, "max": 10, "star_count": 3.5, "value": 7.0}, "vendor_count": 0, "has_linewatch": false, "pic": {"large": "https://img2.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2929167591.jpg", "normal": "https://img2.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2929167591.jpg"}, "honor_infos": [], "uri": "douban://douban.com/tv/37561798", "episodes_info": "", "photos": ["https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2928838245.jpg", "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929888516.jpg", "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929888515.jpg", "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929888514.jpg"], "vendor_icons": [], "interest": null, "year": "2026", "card_subtitle": "2026 / 日本 / 剧情 喜剧 / 冲田修一